{"tid":986101,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【寒夜瑟縮天橋𨋢　露宿者被拍片驅趕︰唔好同我講仁義】","createTime":"2019-01-18T07:37:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-18T13:55:02.000Z","uid":225464,"like":8,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"620876823d2cc320e2c927cd217f89726c8ca39b","tid":986101,"uid":225464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T07:37:16.000Z","msg":"<strong>【寒夜瑟縮天橋𨋢　露宿者被拍片驅趕︰唔好同我講仁義】</strong><br />\n<br />\nLINK有片<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190118/bkn-20190118134317781-0118_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190118%2Fbkn-20190118134317781-0118_00822_001.html&d=099CS1sxW8vPw7uDUphh7QRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=fd993c5c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190118/bkn-20190118134317781-0118_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190118/photo/bkn-20190118134317781-0118_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190118140429\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190118%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190118134317781-0118_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190118140429&h=26bdb2b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n你見到又會點反應呢？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n天寒地凍，大家都想躲在被窩取暖，惟露宿者卻難覓棲身之所。近日就有大叔借宿於上水的天橋𨋢中，遭途人趕走。<br />\n<br />\n有網民在其Facebook發布影片，指星期四（17日）清晨5時半行經彩園路行人天橋時，竟發現有大叔睡在升降機內。他直斥︰「小姐返工見到嚇一跳，嚇到唔敢搭電梯&hellip;人人係咁咪天下大亂，此風不可長&hellip;唔使同我講仁義道德，凍就去社會福利處」。<br />\n<br />\n片段可見，該大叔的衣服殘舊破爛，瑟縮躺睡於地上，旁邊放有大包小包的「家當」。拍片者入𨋢欲把趕他走，不斷喝斥︰「起身喇喂，天光喇，有冇搞錯喺度瞓覺！」大叔被叫醒後，呆望拍片者，一言不發直至其離開。<br />\n<br />\n不少網民可憐大叔︰「好慘，要喺架𨋢瞓覺避寒」、「有屋邊個想瞓街」、「可能天氣太凍，咪畀人瞓吓囉」、「呢個阿叔喺上水幾年，要執7仔過期唔要嘅食物食」。<br />\n<br />\n有網民則撐拍片者︰「係慘，但真係會嚇親」、「讓架𨋢畀佢瞓，老人家咪要行樓梯，輪椅人士爬上去呀」。"},{"pid":"61e17daab6d736d27b7a24fd71846d4afe3c8142","tid":986101,"uid":121130,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T13:18:08.000Z","msg":"個個好似你咁訓法  d人教唔知點上落"},{"pid":"569ddfe8a5370e35c72d2dcbfbff4ee2f72a76e2","tid":986101,"uid":4917,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T13:19:56.000Z","msg":"避寒中心無開咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8489d91309c44e2415f9e2c7d20b4265d4331f7","tid":986101,"uid":123456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T13:20:48.000Z","msg":"好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45b7d1fabc28f806205050f8fc24e7320cd61471","tid":986101,"uid":99700,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T13:41:43.000Z","msg":"去避寒中心食杯麵啦 阻住架𨋢唔係慘就大哂架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7edddd7ed300774b302d48505331d7834fb69631","tid":986101,"uid":37666,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T13:53:27.000Z","msg":"識去一定去禮賓府<br />\n走嚟阻住我哋啲小市民做咩啫"},{"pid":"c724edb6f481a111dedf9d81d0824a00cbd047d0","tid":986101,"uid":112124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T13:55:02.000Z","msg":"腥港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}